articles.title: Northern Iowa extends home streak, tops Indiana State 68-60
articles.description: CEDAR FALLS, Iowa (AP) — Austin Phyfe tallied 13 points and 12 rebounds to lift Northern Iowa to a 68-60 win over Indiana State on Tuesday night for the Panthers' ninth consecutive home victory.
articles.content:
